title: CoinTürk
author: CoinTürk
content: Prices in the cryptocurrency market continue to move in line with the upward trend observed throughout the month of December. This positive atmosphere is enabling not only major cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin and Ethereum, but also altcoins to reach record levels that have not been seen in over a year.Read the full article here: https://en.bitcoinhaber.net/the-rise-of-cryptocurrencies-in-december-bitcoin-and-ethereum-reach-record-levels
